Package: BarnebyLives
Type: Package
Title: Tools for collecting digital data on herbarium specimens
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Reed Clark", "Benkendorf", 
           email = "reedbenkendorf2021@u.northwestern.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9178-3087"))
Description: Provides comprehensive tools for botanical collectors working in 
    Western North America. Automates collection of political boundaries (state, 
    county, PLSS), geographic features (mountain ranges, GNIS places), site 
    characteristics (elevation, slope, aspect, geology), and taxonomic validation. 
    Generates herbarium labels and manifests compatible with Symbiota, Darwin Core, 
    and major herbarium data systems. Named after renowned botanist Rupert Charles Barneby.
